Key Match Events: Australia won the match in a thrilling last-over finish
Mitchell Marsh and Tim David formed a crucial partnership to steer Australia to victory
New Zealand's missed catches and poor fielding contributed to their loss
Post-Match Reflections: Mitchell Marsh expressed relief after the narrow win
Mitchell Santner highlighted Australia's powerful batting as key to their success
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was the first of a three-game series before the T20 World Cup
The series will move to Auckland for the next two matches
